room_title: Escape room "Tiki Island" by Escape The Netherworld in Atlanta
room_address: 2076 West Park Place Blvd Stone Mountain, GA 30087
room_description: Your former archeology professor Dr. Jake Graffenburg has invited you to a crazy weekend at his beach house in Maui to celebrate the discovery of ancient artifacts sacred to the god of peace, Lono. When you get to his place just before dawn you are unexpectedly drawn into a struggle between powerful Hawaiian gods battling for dominance! Graffenburg has carefully protected the beach house from both supernatural and human threats with assorted challenges designed to thwart those of evil intent, but they must be solved quickly before a storm summoned by the foul shark god of Molokai washes away the house and everyone in it into a bay filled with ravenous sharks!
